<p id="d1e8068">To take account of strategies which reduce the spread of the disease to a very low level, we supplement Eq. 
 <xref rid="fd3" ref-type="disp-formula">(3)</xref> by introducing an indicator function, 
 <disp-formula id="fd17">
  <label>(17)</label>
  <math id="d1e8081" display="block" altimg="si222.svg">
   <mrow>
    <mi mathvariant="script">I</mi>
    <mrow>
     <mo>(</mo>
     <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">t</mi>
     <mo>)</mo>
    </mrow>
    <mo linebreak="goodbreak">=</mo>
    <mfenced open="{">
     <mrow>
      <mtable align="axis" equalrows="false" columnlines="none" equalcolumns="false" class="array">
       <mtr>
        <mtd class="array" columnalign="left">
         <mn>0</mn>
         <mo>,</mo>
         <mspace width="1em"/>
        </mtd>
        <mtd class="array" columnalign="left">
         <mtext>if </mtext>
         <msub>
          <mrow>
           <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">I</mi>
          </mrow>
          <mrow>
           <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">P</mi>
          </mrow>
         </msub>
         <mo>+</mo>
         <msub>
          <mrow>
           <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">i</mi>
          </mrow>
          <mrow>
           <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">A</mi>
          </mrow>
         </msub>
         <msub>
          <mrow>
           <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">I</mi>
          </mrow>
          <mrow>
           <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">A</mi>
          </mrow>
         </msub>
         <mo>+</mo>
         <msub>
          <mrow>
           <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">i</mi>
          </mrow>
          <mrow>
           <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">S</mi>
          </mrow>
         </msub>
         <msub>
          <mrow>
           <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">I</mi>
          </mrow>
          <mrow>
           <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">S</mi>
          </mrow>
         </msub>
         <mo>&lt;</mo>
         <mn>1</mn>
         <mo>,</mo>
        </mtd>
       </mtr>
       <mtr>
        <mtd class="array" columnalign="left">
         <mn>1</mn>
         <mo>,</mo>
         <mspace width="1em"/>
        </mtd>
        <mtd class="array" columnalign="left">
         <mtext>otherwise</mtext>
         <mo>.</mo>
        </mtd>
       </mtr>
      </mtable>
     </mrow>
    </mfenced>
   </mrow>
  </math>
 </disp-formula>Then, Eq. 
 <xref rid="fd3" ref-type="disp-formula">(3)</xref> is further modified to read, 
 <disp-formula id="fd18">
  <label>(18)</label>
  <math id="d1e8177" display="block" altimg="si225.svg">
   <mrow>
    <mfrac>
     <mrow>
      <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">d</mi>
      <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">S</mi>
     </mrow>
     <mrow>
      <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">d</mi>
      <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">t</mi>
     </mrow>
    </mfrac>
    <mo linebreak="goodbreak">=</mo>
    <mo linebreak="goodbreak">−</mo>
    <mi mathvariant="script">I</mi>
    <mrow>
     <mo>(</mo>
     <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">t</mi>
     <mo>)</mo>
    </mrow>
    <msub>
     <mrow>
      <mi>β</mi>
     </mrow>
     <mrow>
      <mn>0</mn>
     </mrow>
    </msub>
    <mfrac>
     <mrow>
      <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">S</mi>
     </mrow>
     <mrow>
      <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">N</mi>
     </mrow>
    </mfrac>
    <mrow>
     <mo>(</mo>
     <msub>
      <mrow>
       <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">I</mi>
      </mrow>
      <mrow>
       <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">P</mi>
      </mrow>
     </msub>
     <mo>+</mo>
     <msub>
      <mrow>
       <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">i</mi>
      </mrow>
      <mrow>
       <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">A</mi>
      </mrow>
     </msub>
     <msub>
      <mrow>
       <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">I</mi>
      </mrow>
      <mrow>
       <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">A</mi>
      </mrow>
     </msub>
     <mo>+</mo>
     <msub>
      <mrow>
       <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">i</mi>
      </mrow>
      <mrow>
       <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">S</mi>
      </mrow>
     </msub>
     <msub>
      <mrow>
       <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">I</mi>
      </mrow>
      <mrow>
       <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">S</mi>
      </mrow>
     </msub>
     <mo>)</mo>
    </mrow>
    <mo>;</mo>
   </mrow>
  </math>
 </disp-formula>a similar modification applies to the equation for the ‘exposed’ compartment. In this way, once the disease is reduced to a low level in the population, in the sense that 
 <inline-formula>
  <math id="d1e8265" display="inline" altimg="si226.svg">
   <mrow>
    <msub>
     <mrow>
      <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">I</mi>
     </mrow>
     <mrow>
      <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">P</mi>
     </mrow>
    </msub>
    <mo linebreak="goodbreak" linebreakstyle="after">+</mo>
    <msub>
     <mrow>
      <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">i</mi>
     </mrow>
     <mrow>
      <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">A</mi>
     </mrow>
    </msub>
    <msub>
     <mrow>
      <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">I</mi>
     </mrow>
     <mrow>
      <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">A</mi>
     </mrow>
    </msub>
    <mo linebreak="goodbreak" linebreakstyle="after">+</mo>
    <msub>
     <mrow>
      <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">i</mi>
     </mrow>
     <mrow>
      <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">S</mi>
     </mrow>
    </msub>
    <msub>
     <mrow>
      <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">I</mi>
     </mrow>
     <mrow>
      <mi mathvariant="bold-fraktur">S</mi>
     </mrow>
    </msub>
    <mo linebreak="goodbreak" linebreakstyle="after">&lt;</mo>
    <mn>1</mn>
   </mrow>
  </math>
 </inline-formula>, an unrealistic resurgence in the disease by a notional ‘fraction of a person’ is ruled out.
</p>
